song.title: Music from 3D Demo
song.info:
Music from 3D Demo by Jay / Redland Prd.
A little remix based on a tune by a true master, Madfreak. My first tune in about four years. Got this fantastic FastTracker prog. from a dear friend. Thanks........
Hope you like the tune............ Greetings to: RUNE PEDERSEN, SILICON, ELWOOD, and MADFREAK....
